gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 146, Wizards 128
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeat the Wizards, 146-128. Joel Embiid led the 76ers with 48 points, 11 rebounds, and six assists, including 29 points on 100% shooting in the 3rd quarter. Tyrese Maxey totaled 22 points and a career-high 11 assists as Tobias Harris added 18 points, five rebounds, and five assists. Kyle Kuzma led the Wizards with 28 points, six rebounds, and four assists. Philadelphia improves to 5-1 as Washington moves to 1-5 on the year.
